'''湯尼·李·克隆寧格'''（{{lang-en|Tony Lee Cloninger}}，{{bd|1940年|8月13日|2018年|7月24日|catIdx=Cloninger}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手。生涯曾效力過勇士、紅人與紅雀。

==球員生涯==
克隆寧格於1961年登上大聯盟。1965年，他拿下生涯新高的24勝、211次三振與3.29的防禦率。

不僅投球能力出色，克隆寧格在打擊上也不遜色。他生涯的打擊率為1成92，並敲出11轟與67分打點。其中他在1966年就敲出5轟。

1966年7月3日，勇士以17比3大勝巨人。克隆寧格在那場比賽敲出2支滿貫砲，單場拿下9分打點。他不僅寫下了勇士隊使個人單場打點紀錄，<ref>{{cite web |title=Single Game Records - Atlanta Braves |url=https://www.mlb.com/braves/history/single-game-records |website=MLB.com |accessdate=2020-10-03 |archive-date=2020-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011230111/https://www.mlb.com/braves/history/single-game-records |dead-url=no }}</ref>而他也是[[美國職棒大聯盟單場滿貫砲數排行榜|國聯第一位也是唯一一位能夠單場雙響滿貫砲的投手]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=Tony Cloninger Stats |url=https://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=clonito01 |website=Baseball Almanac |accessdate=2020-10-03 |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922101908/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/players/player.php?p=clonito01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1968年6月11日，勇士隊將克隆寧格、Clay Carroll和Woody Woodward交易至紅人，換來Milt Pappas、Bob Johnson和Ted Davidson。<ref>[https://www.newspapers.com/clip/28272634/the-cincinnati-enquirer/ "Pappas Traded in Big Deal for Atlanta Pitcher," ''The Cincinnati Enquirer'', Wednesday, June 12, 1968.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/28272634/the-cincinnati-enquirer/ |date=20201021135401 }} Retrieved April 30, 2020</ref>最後一年他加入紅雀隊，球季結束後退休。

==教練生涯==
退休後，克隆寧格在1992年加入洋基隊擔任牛棚教練。他也在洋基隊拿下4次世界大賽冠軍。

2002年，紅襪隊將克隆寧格挖角，讓他擔任投手教練。不過他在隔年因為膀胱癌而暫時退出紅襪隊。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.shelbystar.com/sports/cloninger-48236-yankees-reflects.html |title=Whisnant, Gabe, '"Cloninger Reflects on Tenure with Steinbrenner's Yankees", ''The Shelby Star'', July 16, 2010 |access-date=2020-10-05 |archive-date=2010-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100721000538/http://www.shelbystar.com/sports/cloninger-48236-yankees-reflects.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2004年起，克隆寧格便擔任紅襪隊的球員發展顧問，並一路擔任到他去世為止。

克隆寧格曾在2002年面對金鶯隊的一場比賽中遭到驅逐出場，原因是兩隊發生板凳清空衝突時，61歲的克隆寧格不顧危險，直接衝向金鶯隊抓著球員Brook Fordyce使出鎖喉技。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Christensen |first1=Joe |title=O's, Red Sox clear benches, but not the air |url=https://www.baltimoresun.com/news/bs-xpm-2002-07-29-0207290162-story.html |accessdate=2020-07-31 |publisher=The Baltimore Sun |date=2002-07-29 |archive-date=2021-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620224310/https://www.baltimoresun.com/news/bs-xpm-2002-07-29-0207290162-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=MLB Photo Gallery |url=http://www.mlb.com/mlb/photogallery/photos_best/page_08.jsp |website=MLB.com |accessdate=2020-07-31 |archive-date=2020-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009065320/http://www.mlb.com/mlb/photogallery/photos_best/page_08.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Orioles, Red Sox empty benches |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GOFnmRJnxsk |website=YouTube |accessdate=2020-07-31 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123111315/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GOFnmRJnxsk |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==逝世==
2018年7月24日，77歲的克隆寧格在北卡州丹佛去世。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Walker |first1=Richard |title=Local athletic icon Tony Cloninger dies at 77 |url=http://www.gastongazette.com/sports/20180726/local-athletic-icon-tony-cloninger-dies-at-77 |website=GastonGazette.com |accessdate=2018-07-27 |date=2018-07-26 |archive-date=2020-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201014172322/https://www.gastongazette.com/sports/20180726/local-athletic-icon-tony-cloninger-dies-at-77 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
